				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: I do NOT like the new bazaar<a name="73419"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 18 05 2:03 PM</span></td>
