				<td colspan="2"><span>The design is certainly odd, and I don't have any idea *why* they felt the need to change it.  The old version was perfectly functional.
<br />

<br />
On the other hand, it's no more difficult to deal with than the old one was.  I've always used the Find Trader function, which continues to work just fine.  Listening to the folks who spend all their time there, it has cut down on the lag considerably.  You can even shut off the Hide All Traders function and still move.
<br />

<br />
Give it some time, you'll get used to it.
<br />

<br />
Oddly enough, Selo worked fine for me in the New Improved version...  and with a bank in the center of each of the hubs, with the traders in the rooms radiating out from it, the bankers are actually closer to the majority of traders now than they were.
<br />

<br />
On the server I play on, the Arena was almost always entirely deserted.  I doubt anyone will miss it.</span></td>
